## Source (id: 3d1f8a52-0000-4000-8000-000000000001, kind: unknown)

Title: OKF Announcement

<source_markdown>
The specification is published as draft v0.1.
</source_markdown>

Synthesize the next revision of "open-knowledge-format" from the current page and this source."
`;

